fields.name: Apple Developing trees
fields.comment:
A Strategy for young and developing Apple trees.
No water induced stress to maximize growth

fields.name: Apple early season deficit
fields.comment:
A strategy for vigorous trees.
Designed to impart some water stress earlier in the season to slow or stop vegetative growth and shoot growth.
Can assist with ALCM numbers by reducing shoot tips.

Very dependent on soil type and seasonal rainfall. Heavier soils will most likely not deficit sufficiently to induce water stress early season particularly if if combination with rainfall.

fields.name: Grapes Developing
fields.comment:
Strategy for developing grape vines.
Drop in soil moisture after flowering down to version to get developing roots system to hunt and expand root zone- but not strong water induced stress

fields.name: Envy
fields.comment: pan at 40cm- be careful not to over recommend
